title: Mets to start rookie Noah Syndergaard in Game 2 of NLCS (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,338 Mets to start rookie Noah Syndergaard in Game 2 of NLCS (Yahoo Sports) NEW YORK (AP) -- Rookie Noah Syndergaard will start for the New York Mets in Game 2 of the NL Championship Series against the Chicago Cubs on Sunday night.
